## ğŸ“˜ Overview
This repository contains files and documentation for the AWS re/Start Lab focused on **Amazon EC2**.  
In this lab, we launched, configured, monitored, and terminated an EC2 instance while enabling termination protection.

---

## ğŸ¯ Objectives
By completing this lab, you will be able to:
- Launch a web server with termination protection enabled  
- Monitor your EC2 instance  
- Modify the security group to allow HTTP access  
- Resize the EC2 instance to scale  
- Test termination protection  
- Terminate your EC2 instance  

